            <paragraph>The current state of the random number generator. Save and restore this property to restore the generator to a previous state:</paragraph>
            <literal_block force="False" language="gdscript" linenos="False" xml:space="preserve">var rng = RandomNumberGenerator.new()
print(rng.randf())
